The service was OUTSTANDING!
Our server John even had such a wonderful Italian accent when pronouncing the true to Italian specials :) the cook came by more than once to ask how we liked our pizza!
The atmosphere was comfortable, neatly decorated and not to big.
I highly recommend brick oven pizza from this place if you are in downtown.
